<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     5. KEY CONSIDERATIONS (Tabs)
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="cd-tabs">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Key Considerations for Quality Assurance</h2>
    <div class="cd-tabs__wrap">
      <div class="cd-tabs__nav">
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="1">Early Involvement<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
        <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="2">Comprehensive Coverage<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="3">Continuous Testing<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="4">Adaptability<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
        <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="5">Documentation<i class="fas fa-chevron-right tab-arrow"></i></button>
      </div>
      <div class="cd-tabs__content">
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="1">
          <p>The earlier QA is involved in a project, the better. We work alongside your development team from the start, reviewing requirements and designs to catch potential issues before they ever make it into code.</p>
          <p>This proactive approach reduces the cost and time required to fix bugs later in the process and helps ensure your product is built on a solid foundation from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-panel active" data-panel="2">
          <p>Quality assurance isn't just about finding bugs, it's about ensuring every aspect of your application works as intended. Our comprehensive testing approach covers functionality, performance, security, usability, and compatibility across devices and platforms.</p>
          <p>By examining your application from every angle, we help ensure that nothing slips through the cracks, giving you confidence that your product is ready for real-world use.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="3">
          <p>Quality assurance shouldn't be a one-time event before launch. We integrate testing into your continuous development pipeline, running automated tests with every code change to catch issues as soon as they're introduced.</p>
          <p>This continuous approach helps your team move faster with confidence, knowing that regressions and bugs are caught early rather than discovered after release.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="4">
          <p>Every project has unique requirements, and our QA approach adapts to fit yours. Whether you need a lightweight testing process for a small project or a rigorous, multi-layered strategy for a complex enterprise application, we tailor our methods to match.</p>
          <p>As your product evolves, our testing strategy evolves with it, ensuring continued quality no matter how your application grows or changes direction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-panel" data-panel="5">
          <p>Clear documentation is essential to an effective QA process. We maintain detailed test plans, test cases, and bug reports that give your team full visibility into what has been tested, what passed, and what needs attention.</p>
          <p>This documentation also serves as a valuable resource for future development, making it easier to onboard new team members and maintain consistent quality standards over time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

